Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:07.52,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:14.70,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:22.87,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:28.96,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:35.72,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:42.24,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:50.11,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.86,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:58.53,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:06.71,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.67,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:21.01,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:27.81,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
